            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-35452289-864d-4a6a-868b-e8edd0f6f1eb" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
